    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/a7f42708535b86e3d27bceffe51fe36b.poster.avif?t=1666183100\" width=680 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/a7f42708535b86e3d27bceffe51fe36b.webm?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/a7f42708535b86e3d27bceffe51fe36b.mp4?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>在这里查看游戏的序章故事 - 它也是关于赤焰钢铁宇宙计划延伸的一款免费试玩版游戏!</strong><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/590961686096a637f6900603057637e1.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=173 /></span><br><br>赤焰钢铁是一款基于回合制战术的Roguelike机甲RPG类游。管理一队容易过热的老科技技术造的机甲，更热的热度意味着更大的脆弱性和易损性！在你从一个节点旅行到另一个节点的过程中，悉心解开星系生活中一段又一段的故事，不断改良机甲质量，招募新的飞行员，并击败一个又一个有感知能力的人工智能领主！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/f132799f2d1f84b716d115aecc328683.poster.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/f132799f2d1f84b716d115aecc328683.webm?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/f132799f2d1f84b716d115aecc328683.mp4?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/63c188d0b4557ade5184b8e61e30aeda.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=173 /></span><br><br>攻击和移动机甲都需要能量，从而会使机甲产生过热现象。如果温度过高，机甲就会易损，同时也更易受到敌人的攻击。游戏玩法的一个关键元素是在伤害力和脆弱性之间找到完美的平衡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/acc3bca033288226693ce36b1e937091.poster.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/acc3bca033288226693ce36b1e937091.webm?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/acc3bca033288226693ce36b1e937091.mp4?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/e57bff67b4dbc458cb2c9e3e01b27be2.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=173 /></span><br><br>来自宇宙各个角落的飞行员自愿加入赤焰钢铁计划，每个人都带来了他们独特的个性和战术。随着赤焰钢铁计划重新获得对银河系的掌控，新的飞行员将加入对抗PharOS的事业。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/ef8aae14faeff9d87374353aa144db8d.poster.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/ef8aae14faeff9d87374353aa144db8d.webm?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/ef8aae14faeff9d87374353aa144db8d.mp4?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/fbd6302f4a8baddcf12c71fb06f92b26.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=173 /></span><br><br>共有3种类型的机甲：巨无霸、潜行者和标枪，每一种都有自己的优势及反击方式。机甲是用独特的模块制造的，每个模块都有自己的用途。随着赤焰钢铁计划一步步地解放银河系，他们将有机会获得和购买具有独特特性的新模块。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/d3753e1033595c2be066956289eb5a53.poster.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/d3753e1033595c2be066956289eb5a53.webm?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/d3753e1033595c2be066956289eb5a53.mp4?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/862eec2ecc9dd000bd458c5ac302c163.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=173 /></span><br><br>星系中充满了截然不同的行星和故事。通过从一个节点跳到另一个节点，赤焰钢铁计划将引出星系中的各个故事，并为机组人员不断增添新的模块及飞行员。在每一次游戏时都会有新的行星、飞行员、模块、事件以及任务!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/2057775a35b2e7ec799bb65178c5bab7.poster.avif?t=1666183100\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/2057775a35b2e7ec799bb65178c5bab7.webm?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550740/extras/2057775a35b2e7ec799bb65178c5bab7.mp4?t=1666183100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
